<%- include('partials/header') %>

<div class="container page-container">
    <h1 class="page-title">
        <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
        How It Works
    </h1>

    <div class="how-it-works">
        <div class="step-section">
            <h2>File Sharing</h2>
            <div class="steps">
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">1</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Upload Your Files</h3>
                        <p>Go to the Upload page and select up to 10 files (20MB each) from your device. You can drag and drop or click to browse.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">2</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Get Your Link</h3>
                        <p>After uploading, you'll receive a unique shareable link that you can send to anyone.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">3</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Share & Download</h3>
                        <p>Recipients can use the link to view and download your files. No registration required!</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step-section">
            <h2>Text Sharing</h2>
            <div class="steps">
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">1</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Enter Your Text</h3>
                        <p>Navigate to Text Share and paste or type your text content in the provided area.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">2</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Share Instantly</h3>
                        <p>Click share to generate a unique link. Your text is now accessible to anyone with the link.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step-section">
            <h2>Private Sharing</h2>
            <div class="steps">
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">1</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Set a Secret Key</h3>
                        <p>Choose Private Share and create a secret key that recipients will need to access your content.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">2</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Upload Content</h3>
                        <p>Upload your files or enter text. The content will be protected by your secret key.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">3</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Share the Key</h3>
                        <p>Share the secret key with intended recipients. They'll use it to access your private content.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-section">
            <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>How long do files stay available?</h3>
                <p>All content expires 60 minutes after the last access. Each time someone views the content, the timer resets.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>Is there a file size limit?</h3>
                <p>Yes, each file can be up to 20MB, and you can upload a maximum of 10 files at once.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>Do I need to register?</h3>
                <p>No! ShareInAir doesn't require any registration. Just upload and share.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>Is private sharing really secure?</h3>
                <p>Private content is protected by your secret key. Only people with the exact key can access it.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>